THIRD-PARTY DATA AND COMPONENTS
------------------------------
The Software retrieves data from the Semantic Scholar Academic Graph API,
operated by the Allen Institute for Artificial Intelligence (AI2). That data is
NOT covered by this licence. It is governed by the Semantic Scholar API License
Agreement and by the individual licences accompanying the returned data (which
may include CC BY-NC or ODC-BY terms):

    https://www.semanticscholar.org/product/api/license

Operators of the Software are responsible for holding their own Semantic Scholar
API credentials and for complying with those terms, including the requirement to
attribute Semantic Scholar. See DATA-AND-LICENSING.md.

The Software loads Cytoscape.js (MIT licence) and its fcose layout extension
from a public CDN at runtime. Those components remain under their own licences.

